                没错，这就是敌对双方，胜利者书写了历史而已<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p41491063-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







